MultilineDescription.SourceString: Level 1 : Increases damage resistance based on Constructor Site Rating.
MultilineDescription.LocalizedString: Level 1 : Increases damage resistance based on Constructor Site Rating.

MultilineDescription.SourceString: Level 2 : Total Integration : Improves the effectiveness of Defensive Integration's damage resist bonus by 5% and it's offensive damage by 10%.
MultilineDescription.LocalizedString: Level 2 : Total Integration : Improves the effectiveness of Defensive Integration's damage resist bonus by 5% and it's offensive damage by 10%.

MultilineDescription.SourceString: Level 3 : Increases the critical hit chance of Hammers based on Constructor Site Rating.
MultilineDescription.LocalizedString: Level 3 : Increases the critical hit chance of Hammers based on Constructor Site Rating.

MultilineDescription.SourceString: Level 4 : Reduces the Energy cost of Hammer special attacks by 50%.
MultilineDescription.LocalizedString: Level 4 : Reduces the Energy cost of Hammer special attacks by 50%.

MultilineDescription.SourceString: Level 5 : Increases the damage of Containment Unit and Energized Floors based on Constructor Site Rating.
MultilineDescription.LocalizedString: Level 5 : Increases the damage of Containment Unit and Energized Floors based on Constructor Site Rating.
